data.description: YOU CAN'T BEAT THE LOCATION!! Have the best of both worlds! ASSUMABLE FHA MORTGAGE OF 3.5%!! Immerse yourself in the allure of this stunning 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom home with an inground pool. Nestled on a spacious 0.85-acre corner lot surrounded by natural greenery, this property offers a picturesque escape. Positioned strategically to maximize backyard space, the corner lot allows flexibility for accommodating a boat, RV, or any desired additions, all without the restrictions of an HOA. Modern Updates, presenting a charming kitchen adorned with granite counters, stainless steel appliances. The custom bathrooms boast beautiful finishes. Metal Roof, ensures longevity and protection. Additional features include a recently updated water heater and a detached 2-car garage with 576 sq feet, perfect for antique cars or a workshop. This blend of convenience and lifestyle makes it an ideal opportunity for first-time homebuyers. Right off the Suncoast Parkway for easy access to Tampa. Be at Weeki Wachee Springs in under 10 minutes.
